Qianqiao, how are you still unable to understand?

181
00:14:10,850 --> 00:14:15,360
Zhao Jing has just taken the position as the Alliance Leader of the Five Lakes Alliance, and it is a key moment.

182
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:19,850
