229
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:32,840
To tell you the truth, when I went this time, I didn't have to say much.

230
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:36,450
I just brought out our Five Lakes Alliance's command flag and held it up like this.

231
00:17:36,450 --> 00:17:38,640
