Gang Leader Sha, it's inappropriate to say so.

246
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:28,710
I have only been the leader for several months.

247
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:32,810
Achieving such accomplishment now was not because of me,

248
00:18:32,810 --> 00:18:35,650
but because of everyone here.

249
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:41,850
However, compared to the increasing strength of the Five Lakes Alliance,

250
00:18:41,850 --> 00:18:46,290
I am even more concerned about the two kids who have disappeared without a trace,

251
00:18:46,290 --> 00:18:48,980
Xiaolian and Chengling.

252
00:18:48,980 --> 00:18:53,480
I watched Xiaolian grow up. She is a weak girl who grew up at home.

253
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:56,360
She has never set foot in the martial arts world.

254
00:18:56,360 --> 00:19:01,480
In my opinion, these resentments in the martial arts world should not drag her down.

255
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:05,430
But those two old scoundrels Tao Hong and Lv Liu actually captured her as a hostage.

256
00:19:05,430 --> 00:19:08,140
It is truly despicable.

257
00:19:09,610 --> 00:19:12,050
As for Chengling,

258
00:19:12,050 --> 00:19:16,750
he disappeared with a mystery man after the Heroes Conference.

259
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:19,630
We don't even know if he is still alive.

260
00:19:21,520 --> 00:19:25,870
Here, I plead for your help

261
00:19:25,870 --> 00:19:29,660
to find those two kids.

262
00:19:29,660 --> 00:19:32,670
Even if it will cost me everything,

263
00:19:32,670 --> 00:19:35,460
I will not hesitate.

264
00:19:35,460 --> 00:19:38,520
- Leader, please rest assured.
- Please rest assured.

265
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:41,650
That's right! Even if we must turn the martial arts world upside down,

266
00:19:41,650 --> 00:19:44,220
we will definitely bring back those two kids,

267
00:19:44,220 --> 00:19:47,710
dead or alive.

268
00:19:47,710 --> 00:19:49,460
Old Sha!

269
00:19:50,650 --> 00:19:54,730
I misspoke again. I deserve to be slapped.

270
00:19:57,090 --> 00:19:59,470
A'Xiang.

271
00:19:59,470 --> 00:20:01,880
Is Yu Qiufeng inside?

272
00:20:03,010 --> 00:20:05,030
What kind of drug did he give you?

273
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:07,970
The sisters in the Department of the Unfaithful have told me all about that unfaithful man.

274
00:20:07,970 --> 00:20:10,920
Why are you still with him?

275
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:13,540
A'Xiang, lower your voice.

276
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:17,240
The situation in Yueyang City is chaotic now. Master is still not in her right mind yet,

277
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:20,720
and both of us have weak martial arts skills, so we have no way of taking her away.

278
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:22,640
We still need to stay here for now.

279
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:25,770
That's utter nonsense. With your amazing transformation skills,

280
00:20:25,770 --> 00:20:28,940
we can easily disguise ourselves as others. Wouldn't that fool others into letting us leave the city?

281
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:31,330
When we meet up with those old ghosts, I'll let them

282
00:20:31,330 --> 00:20:33,650
rip that Yu guy into ten thousand pieces.

283
00:20:33,650 --> 00:20:35,610
A'Xiang, you don't understand.

284
00:20:35,610 --> 00:20:38,020
The Top Ten Evil Ghosts scheme against one another.

285
00:20:38,020 --> 00:20:41,790
They are trying to kill one another to gain power every single day.

286
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:44,490
This is especially true of us women.

287
00:20:45,610 --> 00:20:48,830
All these years, we've depended on our master's strong martial arts

288
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:53,370
and the Chief of the Valley's protection in order to stay safe.

289
00:20:54,370 --> 00:20:57,800
Now that Master has been unconscious, I'm afraid...

290
00:20:57,800 --> 00:20:59,210
Why fear?

291
00:20:59,210 --> 00:21:02,070
I don't think they have the guts. If they dare to bully us,

292
00:21:02,070 --> 00:21:04,600
Master will chop them up to feed the dogs.

293
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:09,030
However, distant water cannot put out a nearby fire unless you can find Chief.

294
00:21:11,350 --> 00:21:15,570
Only he can find me. Where on earth am I supposed to find him?

295
00:21:16,220 --> 00:21:19,550
I've already asked the sisters in the Department of the Unfaithful to go down the mountain to search for him.

296
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:22,160
There are many of them, and they are leaving marks everywhere.

297
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:25,280
If the Chief meets them, he will naturally contact us.

298
00:21:25,280 --> 00:21:27,170
This is not a solution.

299
00:21:27,170 --> 00:21:31,390
This is a big world, who knows when Master will see them?

300
00:21:31,390 --> 00:21:35,220
For each day that Master doesn't show up, are you and Aunt Luo going to stay here?

301
00:21:35,220 --> 00:21:37,980
Is that Yu Qiufeng reliable?

302
00:21:38,740 --> 00:21:41,810
Don't worry, I can deal with him.

303
00:21:41,810 --> 00:21:43,320
I don't believe you.

304
00:21:43,320 --> 00:21:46,860
You've been drugged by that bastard and won't have the heart to leave him.

305
00:21:46,860 --> 00:21:50,690
If we had known this earlier, when you first entered the valley,

306
00:21:50,690 --> 00:21:53,350
Master and Aunt Luo should have made you drink that Water of Oblivion to completely forget about that bastard.

307
00:21:53,350 --> 00:21:57,360
Quit talking nonsense. What does a little girl like you know?

308
00:21:58,490 --> 00:22:01,740
Never mind, I won't expose you.

309
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:08,000
So now, do you have any way to save Aunt Luo?

310
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:13,600
I do not. The effects of the Water of Oblivion are strong.

311
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:16,000
Once you've taken it, the greatest taboo

312
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:19,000
is to try and awaken the memories it made you forget.

313
00:22:19,800 --> 00:22:23,600
Master already suffered from dissociation before. She is sometimes better, sometimes worse.

314
00:22:23,600 --> 00:22:27,000
Right now, her mind is more chaotic than an ordinary person's.

315
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:29,100
Then, what can we do?

316
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:33,500
I'll try and figure out a solution for Master's sickness.

317
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:37,200
Right, A'Xiang, is there a reason you came to find me?

318
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:41,200
I was originally coming to say goodbye to you.

319
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:43,300
Cao Weining said he's going back to the Gentle Wind Sword Sect.

320
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:45,500
I'm going back with him.

321
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:48,100
I'm not doing it for him!

322
00:22:48,100 --> 00:22:50,760
I'm... I'm doing it for...

323
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:53,000
the task Master gave me.

324
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:56,700
So that's it. You are usually so thoughtless,

325
00:22:56,700 --> 00:22:58,700
but you've suddenly become mature.

326
00:22:58,700 --> 00:23:01,400
- It turns out that's because—
- Stop saying nonsense!

327
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:04,000
But right now,

328
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:08,700
given your circumstances, how can I leave with ease?

329
00:23:09,600 --> 00:23:13,000
It's nothing, A'Xiang. Go ahead, don't worry.

330
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:15,600
When you turn old, you'll understand.

331
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:17,300
There's no time

332
00:23:17,300 --> 00:23:21,200
more precious than being with the one you love.

333
00:23:23,800 --> 00:23:26,200
Each day counts.

334
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:28,800
Each extra day is a luxury.

335
00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:33,100
You won't care to bother about side issues.

336
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:44,400
Scorpion! You must be tired of waiting.

337
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:46,100
Father!

338
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:49,200
How did the regular meeting go?

339
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:51,200
How else could it go?

340
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:57,000
The Heavenly Wolf Fortress and the Striking Cloud Hall

341
00:23:57,000 --> 00:24:00,200
used to be so arrogant and domineering.

342
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:04,300
Now, they wag their tails and fawn before me.

343
00:24:04,300 --> 00:24:08,600
Not to mention those idiots of the Five Lakes Alliance. If I tell them now to go east,

344
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:11,200
is there anyone who would dare to go west?

345
00:24:14,100 --> 00:24:17,800
The Heavenly Wolf Fortress Chief is said to be so formidable and fierce.

346
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:20,000
I only used a little trick,

347
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:22,200
yet he came down to his knees crying,

348
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:27,000
willingly pledging to serve our Five Lakes Alliance. He was worse than Striking Cloud Hall,

349
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:30,400
which understood the circumstances from the start.

350
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:34,300
Good Son, you have helped me so much.

351
00:24:34,300 --> 00:24:37,600
There are many places that are inconvenient for me to appear,

352
00:24:37,600 --> 00:24:42,000
where you have helped me share the burden and resolve problems. With a son like you,

353
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:44,500
I'm a truly fortunate father.

354
00:24:44,500 --> 00:24:46,600
I am still not good enough.

355
00:24:46,600 --> 00:24:48,800
Otherwise, why would Father

356
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:51,900
never let me appear in public?

357
00:24:51,900 --> 00:24:54,200
When am I not hoping for the same thing?

358
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:57,200
It's just that the Venomous Scorpions

359
00:24:57,200 --> 00:25:00,100
have a bad reputation and are deeply resented.

360
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:02,400
This is not the best time yet.

361
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:06,000
Wait patiently a little longer.

362
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:08,200
I'll listen to whatever Father says.

363
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:13,200
The Immortal Dawn Sect Leader, Bai Qifeng,

364
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:16,400
knows too many things that he shouldn't.

365
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:19,800
Before reconvening the Heroes Conference,

366
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:22,000
I would like to silence him forever.

367
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:24,050
Take some capable assistants

368
00:25:24,050 --> 00:25:26,400
and lead the Ghost Valley to remove them.

369
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:28,200
Don't leave any trouble for the future.

370
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:29,800
I will do as you bid.

371
00:25:31,600 --> 00:25:34,490
What about Long Xiao? Any news?

372
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:39,200
He also knows quite a bit, and he's suddenly disappeared.

373
00:25:40,100 --> 00:25:42,200
I can't rest at ease.

374
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:44,000
There is no news at the moment.

375
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:48,300
According to reason, Long Xiao would not leave without saying goodbye.

376
00:25:48,300 --> 00:25:50,200
I'm afraid he was kidnapped.

377
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:52,000
But don't worry, Father.

378
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:54,100
I already sent people to investigate.

379
00:25:54,100 --> 00:25:55,900
I imagine

380
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:59,640
I will hear back soon.

381
00:26:09,800 --> 00:26:13,600
Long Xiao, who prompted you to tell

382
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:15,700
those lies at the Heroes Conference?

383
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:21,800
Are you going to talk or not? If not, I'll kick you down.

384
00:26:21,800 --> 00:26:25,200
Let's see if those children recognize you as their father.

385
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:29,200
Long Xiao, you are a descendant of Elder Long.

386
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:31,000
We don't wish to force you.

387
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:33,900
No, I don't recognize him as my father. I refuse to!

388
00:26:33,900 --> 00:26:36,200
I refuse to!

389
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:50,400
He gave me this body. I'll return it to him now!

390
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:53,300
I refuse to tell you!

391
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:57,400
Even if I die, I won't tell you!

392
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:24,200
By principle, this beast deserves to die a hundred times.

393
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:26,900
But he is Elder Long's only descendant.

394
00:27:43,100 --> 00:27:46,920
[Grave of Master Long Que]

395
00:27:49,330 --> 00:27:53,930
Let's first go to the library stacks to find the maps and look for a way out.

396
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:58,400
Chengling, in the future, you must double your efforts.

397
00:27:58,400 --> 00:28:02,640
You must carry forward Uncle Long's mechanical art.

398
00:28:08,140 --> 00:28:11,260
[Grave of Master Long Que]

399
00:28:15,800 --> 00:28:18,200
Elder, you've returned.

400
00:28:26,970 --> 00:28:28,970
Let's go first.

401
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:40,200
That's the Sword Immortal of Changming Mountain's descendant

402
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:43,600
and the guys who kidnapped Zhang Chengling.

403
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:45,400
Damn it!

404
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:50,000
Why would these people appear together at Dragon Pool Valley?

405
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:52,400
I must send a message to Scorpion King as soon as possible.

406
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:57,500
[Grave of Master Long Que]

407
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:09,000
Slow down! What is that old monster murmuring about? I want to listen.

408
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:13,300
Don't listen. Let's go take a walk nearby.

409
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:18,000
- Uncle Wen!
- I haven't heard enough yet!

410
00:29:20,100 --> 00:29:24,300
Master. Uncle Wen. Where are we going?

411
00:29:27,230 --> 00:29:29,300
I don't know where your Sister Xiang has gone.

412
00:29:29,300 --> 00:29:32,500
However, that girl is very smart. We shouldn't have to worry about her.

413
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:36,000
After the trouble at Mount Jun, the Five Lakes Alliance will surely be unable to recover.

414
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:39,000
Those brave men of the martial arts world must all be dejected, too.
(T/N: idiom, their heads and faces covered with dust)

415
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:41,600
It should be fun to see.

416
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:48,100
You're wearing too little. Have you caught a cold?

417
00:29:50,100 --> 00:29:53,200
Your master's body really is like a beautiful match.

418
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:55,400
As soon as the wind blows, he's out.

419
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:58,600
A'Xu, when things have settled,

420
00:29:58,600 --> 00:30:01,800
we should find a place where all four seasons are like spring.

421
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:04,200
Somewhere warm to grow old.

422
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:07,400
Chengling, where would you like to go?

423
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:09,500
Wherever Master goes, I'll go.

424
00:30:10,190 --> 00:30:11,980
No more waiting.

425
00:30:15,300 --> 00:30:19,200
Let's go back to the Four Seasons Mountain Villa together.

426
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:21,400
Four Seasons Mountain Villa?

427
00:30:24,300 --> 00:30:28,800
What? You're impatient to bring your disciple to pay respects to your master?

428
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:31,300
Bringing such a foolish disciple back,

429
00:30:32,600 --> 00:30:36,500
are you not afraid that your master will be turning in anger in the underworld?

430
00:30:36,500 --> 00:30:38,800
It's our master.

431
00:30:38,800 --> 00:30:41,000
What relationship do you and I have?

432
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:43,400
When did it become "our"?

433
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:45,600
If you keep losing your head like this,

434
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:49,600
I'll have to discipline you on our master's behalf.

435
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:53,800
Master. Uncle Wen. What are you two talking about?

436
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:57,700
In the future, you can't call him "Uncle Wen" anymore.

437
00:30:57,700 --> 00:31:00,000
You should call him Junior Master.

438
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:04,000
Junior Master.

439
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,800
Who's your Junior Master?

440
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:09,200
A'Xu, your disciple is foolish enough already. Don't tease him.

441
00:31:10,900 --> 00:31:15,200
Junior Brother, are you still unwilling to recognize me (as your Senior Brother)?

442
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:17,200
What nonsense are you saying?

443
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:20,600
Heaven treated me unfairly for half my life.

444
00:31:21,300 --> 00:31:24,400
Now, it has finally shown me great benevolence.

445
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:28,000
I alone was all that remained of the Four Seasons Mountain Villa.

446
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:32,700
I never thought I would gain this disciple

447
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:35,700
and find you again.

448
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:42,300
In the underworld, Master can finally be at peace.

449
00:31:48,600 --> 00:31:51,000
- Mother!
- Miaomiao!

450
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:54,700
- Mother!
- Miaomiao!

451
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:57,400
Yan'er, don't be afraid.

452
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:17,300
[White Clothes]

453
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:31,600
Eldest Brother Qin, if not for your arrival at the perfect time,

454
00:32:31,600 --> 00:32:35,700
the fate of my entire family would've been unthinkable.

455
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:38,400
For your great kindness, I...

456
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:41,000
Shut up! You bookworm.

457
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:44,400
What are you saying? Do you not take me for your brother?

458
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,900
Lie down.

459
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:52,800
Don't hurt my father! Don't hurt my father!

460
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:55,200
- Don't hurt my father!
- Yan'er!

461
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:56,400
Yan'er, stop fussing.

462
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:58,900
- Father!
- Come with Mother.

463
00:32:58,900 --> 00:33:01,200
- Father!
- Be good.

464
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:03,800
Father!

465
00:33:03,800 --> 00:33:06,800
I'm sorry. This child

466
00:33:06,800 --> 00:33:12,000
personally witnessed Master breaking my tendons.

467
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:14,000
It scared him.

468
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:18,510
This is ridiculous!

469
00:33:18,510 --> 00:33:22,180
Master was also forced and couldn't help it.

470
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:24,750
My thoughtlessness shouldn't

471
00:33:24,750 --> 00:33:26,890
lead to the destruction of the entire Miracle Healer Valley.

472
00:33:26,890 --> 00:33:29,790
Those people have already become obsessed.

473
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:32,310
If Master wasn't willing to completely break with me,

474
00:33:32,310 --> 00:33:34,270
and draw down the entire Miracle Healer Valley,

475
00:33:34,270 --> 00:33:37,670
then even if I had died, I still—

476
00:33:40,370 --> 00:33:43,410
What exactly did those people come for?

477
00:33:43,410 --> 00:33:46,890
Brother Rong couldn't have made so many enemies singlehandedly.

478
00:33:46,890 --> 00:33:51,000
Moreover, all of you became implicated.

479
00:33:54,210 --> 00:33:56,900
Yan'er, what did I tell you?

480
00:33:56,900 --> 00:33:58,900
Sir Qin is our family's benefactor.

481
00:33:58,900 --> 00:34:01,240
You must not be rude to him.

482
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:04,770
I'm sorry, Mother.

483
00:34:04,770 --> 00:34:07,230
I'm afraid.

484
00:34:09,330 --> 00:34:12,600
Don't be afraid. Mother is here.

485
00:34:14,970 --> 00:34:17,310
Why are you crying?

486
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:19,860
Sister-in-Law,

487
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:25,170
it was so chaotic last night that I didn't get the time to introduce him to you yet.

488
00:34:27,610 --> 00:34:29,330
This is my beloved disciple,

489
00:34:29,330 --> 00:34:32,230
my "Young Forebear" Zhou Zishu.

490
00:34:32,230 --> 00:34:34,980
Master, don't joke.

491
00:34:34,980 --> 00:34:38,940
Heaven and Earth are supreme. Parents and Master are the most respected.

492
00:34:39,450 --> 00:34:43,400
All right, all right. You've collected so many herbs?

493
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:46,430
You've worked hard, our Little Saint Zhou.

494
00:34:47,490 --> 00:34:49,500
Take the little brother outside to play.

495
00:34:49,500 --> 00:34:51,640
Take good care of him.

496
00:34:51,640 --> 00:34:53,550
I don't know how to play.

497
00:34:54,420 --> 00:34:57,580
If you don't even know how to play, what else could you possibly do?

498
00:34:57,580 --> 00:35:01,060
Go ahead. Don't come back until dinnertime.

499
00:35:01,060 --> 00:35:02,810
Little Brother, what is your name?

500
00:35:02,810 --> 00:35:06,080
My name is Zhen Yan.

501
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:08,350
"Zhen Yan" like "needle eye"?
(T/N: "Needle eye" and "Zhen Yan" are homophones)

502
00:35:08,870 --> 00:35:12,650
It's the Yan in Man Yan. It means limitless and free.

503
00:35:12,650 --> 00:35:16,550
All right, I know! It's Zhen Yan.

504
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:19,390
What is its name?

505
00:35:19,390 --> 00:35:22,030
Its name is One Pot.

506
00:35:22,030 --> 00:35:24,120
"One Pot"?

507
00:36:10,780 --> 00:36:13,590
Silly boy. It's me, Mother.

508
00:36:13,590 --> 00:36:17,220
See? How is my transformation skill?

509
00:36:17,220 --> 00:36:19,420
Do you want to learn it?

510
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:23,520
Go inside to check on your father.

511
00:36:32,810 --> 00:36:34,460
Go.

512
00:36:34,460 --> 00:36:38,490
Kneel down in front of Uncle Qin, and kowtow three times.

513
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:54,560
Master, are we taking this little brother home?

514
00:36:54,560 --> 00:36:58,590
Yes. From now on, you'll have a friend.

515
00:36:58,590 --> 00:37:02,500
You two must love and care for each other from now on.

516
00:37:02,500 --> 00:37:05,920
You are the older one, so you should take good care of him. Understand?

517
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:07,650
I definitely will.

518
00:37:09,570 --> 00:37:12,610
Little Brother, we have a lot of delicious food and fun toys.

519
00:37:12,610 --> 00:37:15,720
When you come home with us, I'll bring all of them out to show you.

520
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:17,830
Call him Junior Brother.

521
00:37:18,500 --> 00:37:20,280
Junior Brother.

522
00:37:24,750 --> 00:37:26,620
Are you all right?

523
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:30,510
We are always away most of the time,

524
00:37:30,510 --> 00:37:34,520
our child has been spoiled to be stubborn and unruly.

525
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:39,510
Going forward, I'd like Young Older Brother Zishu to help discipline him.

526
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:42,690
If he does anything wrong, do not hesitate to punish him.

527
00:37:42,690 --> 00:37:47,120
It's just that, please consider how pitiful he is

528
00:37:48,190 --> 00:37:50,150
and not shun him.

529
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:53,600
Father, what do you mean?

530
00:37:53,600 --> 00:37:56,720
Are you not leaving with me?

531
00:37:57,410 --> 00:38:01,220
Twenty years have passed since then.

532
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:05,100
Luckily... Luckily,

533
00:38:06,340 --> 00:38:08,740
I originally thought I wouldn't live long.

534
00:38:08,740 --> 00:38:12,190
I also don't know how much martial arts Chengling can learn from me.

535
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:18,140
Now that I've found you, this is the best arrangement.

536
00:38:18,140 --> 00:38:22,050
Revive the Four Seasons Mountain Villa, take care of Chengling,

537
00:38:22,050 --> 00:38:25,590
and inherit Master's legacy, I can then rest assured.

538
00:38:25,590 --> 00:38:29,050
Master, what do you mean that you won't live long?

539
00:38:29,050 --> 00:38:31,310
Why wouldn't you live long?

540
00:38:31,310 --> 00:38:33,910
Have you finished saying all that nonsense?

541
00:38:33,910 --> 00:38:37,150
Don't shirk your responsibility.

542
00:38:37,150 --> 00:38:38,790
If you want to revive the Four Seasons Mountain Villa, you stay alive and do it yourself.

543
00:38:38,790 --> 00:38:43,990
♫ Who is drunk in their dreams but can't find
the homeland when they wake?  ♫

544
00:38:43,990 --> 00:38:47,890
When you separate the word Yan into two parts, aren't they Ke and Xing?
(T/N: "Yan" = 衍, "Ke Xing" = 客行. The latter can be found in the former)

545
00:38:47,890 --> 00:38:52,370
It's my mistake. I kept thinking you were Elder Rong's descendant.

546
00:38:52,370 --> 00:38:56,880
♫  I don't mind hate and slander, but my melancholy persists ♫

547
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:59,690
You turned out to be my Brother Zhen.

548
00:39:02,410 --> 00:39:04,720
Why did you change your surname to Wen?

549
00:39:07,410 --> 00:39:13,040
♫ Is that our light that appeared out of nowhere? ♫

550
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:14,950
My surname has always been Wen!

551
00:39:14,950 --> 00:39:18,770
Master. Junior Uncle. What are you talking about?

552
00:39:18,770 --> 00:39:21,490
All right, I won't keep asking.

553
00:39:21,490 --> 00:39:23,390
All these years, what exactly happened?

554
00:39:23,390 --> 00:39:25,190
The Zhen family...

555
00:39:26,060 --> 00:39:27,720
Are you all right?

556
00:39:29,490 --> 00:39:31,160
Junior Uncle! Junior Uncle!

557
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:33,110
Chengling, don't chase after him.

558
00:39:33,110 --> 00:39:36,080
Master, Junior Uncle, he...

559
00:39:37,390 --> 00:39:45,950
Wait until he comes back on his own.

560
00:39:45,950 --> 00:39:53,070
♫ The lights of thousands of families light up thousands of hills
The past disappears like smoke waves in a sandstorm ♫

561
00:39:53,070 --> 00:40:01,730
♫ I will clear away my cold past and happily spend the rest
of my life making wine and tea with you ♫

562
00:40:27,870 --> 00:40:34,980
♫ The trees fall boundlessly
as the Yangtze river rolls without end ♫

563
00:40:34,980 --> 00:40:36,650
Too late.

564
00:40:39,660 --> 00:40:41,760
It's too late.

565
00:40:43,120 --> 00:40:50,330
♫ Raise the voice to sing when victorious and rest when not
Unrestrained and unhindered ♫

566
00:40:50,330 --> 00:40:58,010
♫ Gaining a soulmate who can provide comfort
where the wind and dust is helpless ♫

567
00:41:37,330 --> 00:41:43,540
♫ The sky is gray as I cross the cold river,
my duties taken care of ♫

568
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:52,190
♫ Smiling at the absurdity of the moon's reflection in my cup ♫

569
00:41:52,190 --> 00:41:59,280
♫ Who allowed me to roam around the world on horseback? ♫

570
00:41:59,280 --> 00:42:07,820
♫ Who is drunk in their dreams but can't find
the homeland when they wake?  ♫

571
00:42:07,820 --> 00:42:14,790
♫ The cold rain of autumn kisses my windows ♫

572
00:42:14,790 --> 00:42:22,430
♫  I don't mind hate and slander, but my melancholy persists ♫

573
00:42:22,430 --> 00:42:26,150
♫ The spring breeze brings greenery along the river  ♫

574
00:42:26,150 --> 00:42:29,710
♫ But can't warm the ice in my heart ♫

575
00:42:29,710 --> 00:42:37,600
♫ Is that our light that appeared out of nowhere? ♫

576
00:42:37,600 --> 00:42:41,090
♫ I resent being unable to meet you earlier, but it is not too late ♫

577
00:42:41,090 --> 00:42:44,850
♫ Don't let the flowers of the seasons down ♫

578
00:42:44,850 --> 00:42:52,850
♫ Give up the adventures on horseback for a peaceful,
